      Changelog

      spatialGE 1.2.0

      • Functions STenrich, STgradient, and STdiff available.

      spatialGE 1.1.0

      • Multiple, significant changes to STlist (not compatible with STlist objects from version 1.0).

      Contents

      =======

      Definition of an STlist object class.

      STlist-class.Rd

      Definition of an STlist object class.

      Slots

      counts

      per spot RNA counts

      coords

      per spot x,y coordinates

      clinical

      dataframe with metadata per sample

      tr_counts

      transfromed per spot counts

      gene_var

      gene variances and standardized variances

      gene_het

      spatial heterogeneity statistics per gene

      gene_krige

      results from kriging on gene expression

      cell_deconv

      results of ESTIMATE and cell type deconvolution

      cell_krige

      results from kriging on cell type deconvolution scores

      st_clusters

      cluster assignments from STclust

      pheno_plots

      per gene plots of spatial heterogeneity statistics vs metadata variables

      misc

      Parameters and images from ST data
